Meet Onkar Yadav

With over 15 years of experience in stand-up comedy, Onkar Yadav has become one of India's most beloved comedians. His unique blend of observational humor, witty commentary on daily life, and relatable stories has earned him a dedicated following across the country.

From corporate events to comedy clubs, Onkar brings laughter wherever he goes. His performances are known for their clean humor, audience interaction, and unforgettable punchlines that keep people talking long after the show ends.
